<p><strong>Superseded patches:</strong></p>
<p>This patch supersedes Microsoft Security Bulletin <a href="http://technet.microsoft.com/security/bulletin/ms99-002" data-linktype="external">MS99-002</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Verifying patch installation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Please verify using the following methods:
<ul>
